<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero__card">
    <span class="hero__prehead">Your team’s calm and collected HQ</span>
    <h1 class="hero__title">All your projects, activities, and notes under one roof.</h1>
    <p class="hero__lead">
      Campy gives your team the calm clarity of Basecamp with a focused spin for your own projects.
      Plan activities, assign categories, and keep conversations threaded in one friendly workspace.
    </p>
    <div class="hero__cta">
      <%= link_to "Start for free", new_user_registration_path, class: "btn btn--primary" %>
      <%= link_to "See how it works", new_user_session_path, class: "btn btn--ghost" %>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="hero__sparkle"></div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <header class="section__head">
    <h2 class="section__title">What you’ll love</h2>
    <p class="section__lead">
      Borrowed from the spirit of Basecamp’s famous homepage—minus the chaos. Campy keeps things light, bright,
      and approachable so your team actually wants to log in every day.
    </p>
  </header>

  <div class="grid cards">
    <article class="card">
      <h3>Activities > Todos</h3>
      <p class="meta">Group work with categories, due dates, and quick status toggles. Everything is snappy and feels good.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h3>Friendly messaging</h3>
      <p class="meta">Add updates to any activity and keep the discussion right where the work happens—never search Slack again.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h3>Clear owners</h3>
      <p class="meta">Projects live with their owners. Permissions keep the right people in-the-know, automatically.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h3>Reassuring rhythm</h3>
      <p class="meta">A calm visual style, soft shadows, and bright accents inspired by Basecamp remit anxiety and give breathing room.</p>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>
